{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/ideas/christmas-tree-lights-controlled-by-neural-network.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Addressable LEDs in some ornament. A neural network drives the signals. It defines timings and selects what LEDs should be on or off. A camera feed goes to another network which provides feedback for the first network. I propose, instead of designing special algorithm for switching lights or crafting special reward function for reinforcement learning system, it will make decisions based on the visuals it perceives from the camera.</p>\n<p>It essentially creates a closed-loop system where the visual input guides the lighting decisions.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3d-design\" style=\"position:relative;\">3D design<a href=\"#3d-design\" aria-label=\"3d design permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"inspiration\" style=\"position:relative;\">Inspiration<a href=\"#inspiration\" aria-label=\"inspiration permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 